<p>The <code>SummaryListItem</code> is one row inside a
  <a href="/components/summary-list/"><code>SummaryList</code></a>.
  It emits a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> with a <code>&lt;dt&gt;</code>
  for the key and a <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code> for the value, plus an
  optional actions <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code>.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/summary-list/">SummaryList demo</a>
  for the composed example.</p>
